{"tid":1438684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"總之邊個叫停，一定係鬼！解散軍恐怖過解放軍！","createTime":"2019-08-09T23:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T01:30:50.000Z","uid":241151,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"de513ceaef808075d8271229fc4bafe4b8ffa617","tid":1438684,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:47:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9nj9sXU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9nj9sXU.jpg&h=fc5b0865&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過去兩個月  一提泛民過去D仆街野就勁多泛粉入來屌<br />\n又話不分化不割席 什麼兄弟爬山<br />\n屌你老母  爬到半山你抆撚住叫人停<br />\n咁撚樣叫各自爬山呀?<br />\n你地要停咪自己停囉  反正你班仆街都無做過D乜<br />\n　<br />\n總之邊撚個叫停 一撚定係鬼  <br />\n五大訴求未有回應<br />\n義士被捕受罪未撤銷提控 <br />\n烈士殉道政權無視<br />\n真普選未有<br />\n中共未滅<br />\n你班仆街泛民而家叫停   <br />\n係咪收(你地所謂既呀爺)中共指令了?<br />\n　<br />\n解散軍恐怖過解放軍<br />\n泛民出賣港人行先好多年"},{"pid":"7547eac6c8ca02bdb88c5d21404b29524a7da30e","tid":1438684,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:53:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64d282132a004f31502b3b008d5cf4a9b7cb1d32","tid":1438684,"uid":265498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:56:07.000Z","msg":"張圖幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca7663aa9318eb8cc88496c06e3ad73176089d1","tid":1438684,"uid":174174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:16:51.000Z","msg":"應該加多個<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不要停！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b7e3068ad1e15146f0f4fd6ca6ae554f6e7a67","tid":1438684,"uid":118176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:28:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"330b6dd2a1ac26e365fabb483057977d76052601","tid":1438684,"uid":117892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-1